   $ tjmer --help
   usage: tjmer [-h] TIME [COMMAND]

   positional arguments:
     TIME        how long to wait:
                   Nd = N days
                   Nh = N hours
                   Nm = N minutes
                   Ns = N seconds
                 or concatenation of any of the above;
                 or until when to wait:
                   @HH:MM
                   @HH:MM:SS
     COMMAND     command to execute instead of printing BEL

   options:
     -h, --help  show this help message and exit

